{"tid":1457102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（散/留撚入）今次唔係人數 係遊客決定一切","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:09:01.000Z","uid":35637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"87d894022008a78b87fd1d5b6aea5bb64cc8ca22","tid":1457102,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"討論前大家一定要有個前設；<br />\n1.機場好難走 一封你準備係入面過夜<br />\n2. 遊客有光環<br />\n<br />\nBe water<br />\n有遊客就盡地主之誼 介紹香港<br />\n冇遊客唔該好走了<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾人偷換概念<br />\n今日唔會係最後一次和你飛 <br />\n唔好講到得一次機會<br />\n<br />\n當宣布機場唔會再有遊客<br />\n走絕對冇問題<br />\n當宣布機場復飛<br />\n入去就冇問題<br />\n<br />\n但要記住<br />\n遊客一走 冇飛機落<br />\n你介紹唔到香港<br />\n機場就冇意義<br />\n請預留時間俾接機人士同遊客一齊走 趕尾班車<br />\nBe water!"},{"pid":"11ff5040297e3bc42435332d6911e81d05c2b944","tid":1457102,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"811 721"},{"pid":"5e39419cb4d50a3ef419aed6defff8406791076b","tid":1457102,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"811 721"},{"pid":"7a4d765fc3a8b4a7417ab5a4bc7d64931ed64f6c","tid":1457102,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"811721"},{"pid":"c4ca7bdb129cb55fc4edc925dee32e598f2da9e5","tid":1457102,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"811721"},{"pid":"5c8b04dc384889d5746243cf176ed9efd413d57f","tid":1457102,"uid":297666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a7415e3cc7f1d2102d9340f036205565cd83782c","tid":1457102,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"811721"},{"pid":"b6402ad3ccea1d852acd491128c8220214e85f93","tid":1457102,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"811721"},{"pid":"73eb87392bd33acc589aec58d0a218522bb4